Calling all Robotics Enthusiasts!
🤖 DJSCE Robotics and Automation Society (RAS) Committee is thrilled to announce a captivating seminar on Robot Operating System (ROS) featuring renowned speaker, Mr. Gaurav Chaudhary(Principal Software Engineer). 🤖

Mark your calendars!
🗓: 12th April, 2024 (Friday)
⏰: 12:30 PM
📍: Seminar Hall (DJSCE)

What is ROS?
ROS is an open-source operating system specifically designed for robot development. This seminar is a fantastic opportunity to:
- Gain a comprehensive understanding of ROS fundamentals.
- Learn from an industry expert.

Don't miss out on this  chance to delve into the exciting world of ROS! Share this message with your fellow robotics enthusiasts!✨

#robot #automation #society #operatingsystem

🚀 "Industrial visits spark the flames of creativity and foster out-of-the-box thinking." 🔥✨ At DJS RAS, we wholeheartedly believe in this mantra, and what better way to kick off our journey than with our first event of 2023-24!! 🎉
🌐 We took an exhilarating plunge into the realm of plastics manufacturing at AIPMA AMTEC on October 25th. 💡💼 🌟 The All India Plastics Manufacturers' Association (AIPMA), with its 75-year legacy, stands as a testament to industry visionaries. 🏭🔗 It's not just an association; it's a pioneer in the Plastic Industry, continually expanding and progressing🌈✊.
The event was a fusion of knowledge and fun, creating a memorable experience for both the students and organizers alike. 🤝🎓 We're charged up and eagerly anticipate curating more such enriching events for our dynamic student community in the future. 🚀🔍 #DJSRAS #IndustrialVisit #PlasticsIndustryExploration #FutureLeadership

🔧 Uncover the future of engineering with our Industrial Visit to AIPMA AMTEC! 🔧

🚀 Witness real-world applications of classroom knowledge.
🔍 Gain insights into cutting-edge technologies and processes.
🛠 Interact with industry experts and professionals.

Join us on Oct 25th for an exclusive Industrial Visit. 🔥🚀

Witness innovation, connect with experts, and explore your engineering journey. 🌐

#EngineeringExcellence #InnovationJourney
#IndustrialVisit
#DJSRAS
